# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:11
translate chinese tammy1b_e3683166:

    # "Tammy is supposed to be here, so I park and walk up to the boxing club."
    "塔米应该在这里，所以我把车停好，走向拳击俱乐部。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:12
translate chinese tammy1b_645ac8a9:

    # "The place is not very busy, with only a few people training."
    "这里人不多，只有几个人在训练。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:13
translate chinese tammy1b_4394a883:

    # "As soon as I walk in, all eyes turn to me though. They stare at me, unwelcoming."
    "可我刚一进门，所有人的目光就都转向了我。他们盯着我，神情冷淡。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:14
translate chinese tammy1b_29926d95:

    # "Until Tammy speaks up."
    "直到塔米开口。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:17
translate chinese tammy1b_9f753069:

    # tm "Don't worry guys, he's with me."
    tm "别担心，各位，他是和我一起来的。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:18
translate chinese tammy1b_671e6fc9:

    # tm "Hey, [pcname]. Glad you came. Ready to get your workout on?"
    tm "嘿，[pcname]。很高兴你来了。准备好开始锻炼了吗？"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:19
translate chinese tammy1b_bcae12a9:

    # pc "Sure, let's do this."
    pc "当然，咱们开始吧。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:20
translate chinese tammy1b_249f802e:

    # tm "Locker room is in the back. Go change into your workout gear and meet me by the bench press."
    tm "更衣室在后面。去换上运动服，然后在卧推架那儿找我。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:23
translate chinese tammy1b_9d33ab78:

    # "I do as she says and head to the locker room in the back of the place. I change into my gym shorts and a muscle shirt and walk back up front to join her."
    "我照她说的去做，走向场地后方的更衣室。换上运动短裤和紧身背心后，我走回前台和她汇合。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:26
translate chinese tammy1b_5c6e9d09:

    # tm "Alright, looking good there, [pcname]. You're not in bad shape, but look like you could use a little more muscle."
    tm "“行，这身打扮不错，[pcname]。你的身材还行，但看起来肌肉再多一点会更好。”"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:27
translate chinese tammy1b_40793a0e:

    # tm "How much do you lift?"
    tm "“你平时能举多少重量？”"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:28
translate chinese tammy1b_cf4776aa:

    # pc "I'm not sure. I haven't been to the gym since high school."
    pc "“我不确定。自从高中毕业后我就没去过健身房了。”"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:29
translate chinese tammy1b_68f22cd1:

    # tm "Wow, how do you keep a body like that without working out?"
    tm "哇，不锻炼怎么能保持这样的身材？"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:30
translate chinese tammy1b_a5cfcbe8:

    # pc "I don't know, just stay busy I guess?"
    pc "我也不知道，大概就是一直很忙吧？"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:31
translate chinese tammy1b_ccc6b955:

    # tm "Well, good job on that."
    tm "嗯，做得不错。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:32
translate chinese tammy1b_4f70adfd:

    # tm "Here, spot me and I'll show you the proper way to do this, just as a reminder. Then we can figure out how much you can bench."
    tm "来，帮我扶一下，我给你演示一下正确的动作，作为提醒。然后我们可以测测你能卧推多少。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:35
translate chinese tammy1b_c0d9e914:

    # "I stand over her while she demonstrates the proper bench press technique."
    "我站在她身旁，看着她演示正确的卧推技巧。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:36
translate chinese tammy1b_806df103:

    # "She breathes in and out as she pushes the weight up and down, her triceps bulging."
    "她一边推举着杠铃上下移动，一边深呼吸，肱三头肌鼓起。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:37
translate chinese tammy1b_e6fef3d7:

    # "Everything about Tammy is hard and tight - her whole body is a muscle for her to flex."
    "塔米浑身都紧绷有力——她的整个身体就像一块随时可以展示的肌肉。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:38
translate chinese tammy1b_33c443c8:

    # "When she has finished ten reps, I help her put the weight back on its hook."
    "当她完成十组动作后，我帮她把杠铃放回挂钩上。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:42
translate chinese tammy1b_c0183d90:

    # tm "Alright, now your turn."
    tm "好了，现在轮到你了。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:43
translate chinese tammy1b_4a711d57:

    # tm "Start with what I was lifting. You should be able to handle that, given how much bigger than me you are."
    tm "先从我刚才举的重量开始。以你比我壮实得多，应该能应付得来。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:44
translate chinese tammy1b_63023601:

    # pc "Okay."
    pc "好的。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:47
translate chinese tammy1b_5ddf218a:

    # "We switch positions to where now I am on the bench and she is standing over me."
    "我们换了位置，现在我躺在长凳上，她站在我上方。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:48
translate chinese tammy1b_388a95d1:

    # "I imitate her technique and lift the weight."
    "我模仿她的动作，举起杠铃。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:49
translate chinese tammy1b_1d8c9a1b:

    # "I am surprised at how heavy it is. She hadn't seemed to have much trouble lifting it, but I find myself struggling."
    "我惊讶于它的沉重。她举起来时似乎毫不费力，但我却感到力不从心。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:50
translate chinese tammy1b_0188fccb:

    # tm "Remember your breathing. Push."
    tm "记住呼吸。用力。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:51
translate chinese tammy1b_61239f96:

    # "I try to control my breathing, try to push myself. My muscles ache after only a few reps."
    "我努力控制呼吸，逼自己再加把劲。才做了几组，肌肉就酸痛起来。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:52
translate chinese tammy1b_d6ccb3fd:

    # "I keep pushing, barely making it to 10. Then she pulls the weight back onto the hook for me."
    "我坚持着，勉强做到了10组。然后她帮我把杠铃放回挂钩上。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:56
translate chinese tammy1b_37c438ac:

    # tm "Well you're definitely more out of shape than you look. We're going to need to do a lot more of this."
    tm "看来你的体能确实比看起来差多了。我们还得做很多这样的训练。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:57
translate chinese tammy1b_cf997fe8:

    # pc "You're telling me. Man, I'm hurting."
    pc "你说的对。天啊，我浑身都疼。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:58
translate chinese tammy1b_76be2251:

    # tm "Take a breather and then we'll get started on the other exercises."
    tm "休息一下，然后我们开始做其他练习。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:59
translate chinese tammy1b_2df16e27:

    # pc "Other?"
    pc "其他？"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:62
translate chinese tammy1b_e32e4b37:

    # tm "Uh, yeah. You can't just workout your arms. Gotta do the whole body."
    tm "嗯，是的。不能只练胳膊，得练全身。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:65
translate chinese tammy1b_774f99cb:

    # "I take a rest, then we get back to it, moving around the gym to different areas to do a full-body workout."
    "我休息了一会儿，接着我们又开始训练，在健身房里穿梭到不同区域，进行全身锻炼。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:66
translate chinese tammy1b_07f4d546:

    # "By the end, I am exhausted. Tammy is sweating, but is feeling good. I feel like I might die."
    "练到最后，我累得不行。塔米虽然满头大汗，但感觉不错。我却觉得自己快要死了。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:69
translate chinese tammy1b_ecf18d91:

    # tm "You did good today for a first gym day in a long time."
    tm "今天是你久违的健身首日，表现很不错。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:70
translate chinese tammy1b_bac72fc8:

    # tm "It'll get easier the more you do it. Then you'll have to start looking for new ways to build muscle."
    tm "练得越多，就会越轻松。到时候你得开始寻找新的增肌方法了。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:71
translate chinese tammy1b_2643738c:

    # pc "I don't know about that."
    pc "我不确定。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:72
translate chinese tammy1b_c1b44fe4:

    # tm "Well, I had fun today. You're a pretty good workout partner."
    tm "嗯，今天我玩得很开心。你是个不错的锻炼伙伴。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:73
translate chinese tammy1b_644168c9:

    # tm "Come back and do it again with me sometime. I'm here every afternoon."
    tm "改天再来跟我一起练吧。我每天下午都在这儿。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:74
translate chinese tammy1b_67cf3c55:

    # tm "Or you can come back by yourself. The guys will let you in, now that they know you're with me."
    tm "或者你也可以自己来。既然他们知道你跟我一起，那几个家伙肯定会放你进来的。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:75
translate chinese tammy1b_e43cb525:

    # pc "Okay, I'll do that."
    pc "行，我会来的。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:76
translate chinese tammy1b_e4873b3d:

    # tm "Build up that muscle, [pcname]. Girls love it. You're looking real sexy with that post-workout shine."
    tm "把肌肉练起来，[pcname]。女生都喜欢这个。你那锻炼后泛出的光泽，看起来特别性感。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:79
translate chinese tammy1b_1df8eb68:

    # tm "Anyway, I gotta go shower and get to work."
    tm "不管怎样，我得去冲个澡然后去上班了。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:80
translate chinese tammy1b_2c74ab1f:

    # tm "I'll see you later, [pcname]."
    tm "待会儿见，[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:81
translate chinese tammy1b_53fa2ef6:

    # pc "Okay, see ya."
    pc "好的，待会儿见。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:84
translate chinese tammy1b_85f2c0dc:

    # "We head to the back, to separate showers."
    "我们走向后方，各自去淋浴间。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:85
translate chinese tammy1b_43779587:

    # "By the time I am done washing up, she is already gone."
    "等我洗完澡时，她已经走了。"

# game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:86
translate chinese tammy1b_00b69932:

    # "I leave the gym, my whole body sore, and get in my car."
    "我离开健身房，全身酸痛，坐进车里。"

translate chinese strings:

    # game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:2
    old "Tammy wants you to meet her at the gym on the weekend."
    new "塔米想让你周末去健身房见她。"

    # game/Scenes/Tammy/tammy1b.rpy:3
    old "She'll be there during the morning and afternoon."
    new "她上午和下午都会在那里。"

